# Sparse Bit Array

## Description
A space efficient sparse bit array for Ruby.
Inspired from https://github.com/brettwooldridge/SparseBitSet.

## Assumptions
- Index starts at *zero*

## Usage

```ruby
bit_array = SparseBitArray.new(1000)
bit_array[0] = true
bit_array.set(0)

bit_array[0] # => true

bit_array[0] = false
bit_array.clear(0)

bit_arrayp0] # => false
```
